Class WhiteQuarterSpectrum

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<AbstractVisualization>

    public final class WhiteQuarterSpectrum
extends AbstractSpectrumAnalyzer
    This is a version of the QuarterSpectrum visualization specifically designed to allow direct comparison between the usual spectrum and a whitened spectrum.
